However, against all odds, I hope and pray, that when the day comes, thata foreign entity decides that they have the audacity to invade the U.S.A., that I will have my fellowcountrymen take up whatever arms they can acquire, be it fully automatic rifles, pistols, grenades,dynamite, nitroglycerin, or C4 explosive, and help me and my comrades defend what we believeis right and just.
